{"tid":1952540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解周同學會走入停車場,係因為佢想幫手做哨。點解佢想做哨,係因為佢想令大家知道班狗嘅即時部署","createTime":"2020-03-31T16:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T09:08:32.000Z","uid":120896,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9896ae38173749b69ec4bcd1e4608e8d5441b307","tid":1952540,"uid":120896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T16:04:43.000Z","msg":"點解佢想令大家知道班狗嘅即時部署,係因為佢想大家不被捕<br />\n<br />\n結果,班唔知真五毛定冷氣軍師不斷情緒勒索,講埋啲咩冇人去現場悼念就係當手足CONDOM,就係忘記件事,將抗爭儀式化,水鳩啲手足去現場送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由周同學過身到依家嘅4個8號,夾夾埋埋有過百個手足被捕,完全同周周學出嚟嘅初衷背道而馳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n721,831,922,118...個個月都起碼有4日自動送人頭比班狗,我係狗真係多謝都講唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇智慧嘅抗爭,如一班蠻牛冇目的地衝,注定唔會成功<br />\n<br />\n係,我係散水撚分化撚放負撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e576a54bfcfbdb7dc7fa4a11584acc6f8c9139bd","tid":1952540,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T16:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連apink sir都轉做散水撚"},{"pid":"84dc9f50d96fd46af9f7ca536108ddbb21eb2851","tid":1952540,"uid":120896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T16:08:13.000Z","msg":"我係散水撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4d2a79a7e33ea7eaad5244dc0089c5159fffa3","tid":1952540,"uid":120896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T16:11:32.000Z","msg":"我係分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca61f0b7051ed2df4021a512212d9d9bb9d9123d","tid":1952540,"uid":120896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c